---
layout: base.njk
title: Yoga Types
description: Explore different styles of yoga practice to find your perfect match
---

<section class="page-header">
  <h1>Yoga Types</h1>
  <p>Explore different yoga styles and discover what each practice offers</p>
</section>

<section class="guide-section-container">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="guide-section-wrapper">
      <div class="guide-section-intro">
        <h2>Different Paths, One Practice</h2>
        <p>Yoga encompasses many different styles and approaches, each with its own focus and benefits. Explore the various types below to find the practice that resonates with you.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="guide-selector">
        <div class="guide-selector-buttons">
          {% for type in site.yogaTypes %}
            <button class="guide-selector-btn" data-target="{{ type | slug }}">
              <span>{{ type }}</span>
            </button>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="guide-content-container">
        {% for type in site.yogaTypes %}
          <div class="guide-content-box" id="{{ type | slug }}-content">
            <h2>{{ type }}</h2>
            <div class="yoga-type-content">
              {% if type == "Vinyasa" %}
                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Overview</h3>
                  <p>Flowing sequences that synchronize movement with breath. A dynamic practice that builds heat and endurance.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Philosophy</h3>
                  <p>Focuses on the connection between breath and movement, creating a moving meditation.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Benefits</h3>
                  <p>Improves cardiovascular health, builds strength and flexibility, enhances focus.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Who It's For</h3>
                  <p>Great for those who enjoy movement and flow, athletes looking for cross-training, and practitioners seeking a more active style.</p>
                </div>
              {% elif type == "Hatha" %}
                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Overview</h3>
                  <p>Traditional practice emphasizing basic postures and alignment. Great for beginners and those wanting a slower pace.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Philosophy</h3>
                  <p>Balances opposing forces (sun and moon energy) through physical postures and breathing.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Benefits</h3>
                  <p>Builds foundation, improves posture, increases body awareness and mindfulness.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Who It's For</h3>
                  <p>Perfect for beginners, those recovering from injury, or anyone wanting to focus on proper alignment and fundamentals.</p>
                </div>
              {% elif type == "Yin" %}
                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Overview</h3>
                  <p>Passive practice with long-held poses that target deep connective tissues. Excellent for increasing flexibility.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Philosophy</h3>
                  <p>Works with the body's meridian system to improve energy flow and balance.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Benefits</h3>
                  <p>Increases flexibility, reduces stress, improves joint mobility, complements active practices.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Who It's For</h3>
                  <p>Great for athletes needing recovery, those with tight muscles, and anyone seeking a more meditative, introspective practice.</p>
                </div>
              {% elif type == "Power" %}
                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Overview</h3>
                  <p>Vigorous, fitness-based approach to vinyasa-style yoga. Builds strength, endurance, and flexibility.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Philosophy</h3>
                  <p>Emphasizes strength and intensity while maintaining mindfulness and proper form.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Benefits</h3>
                  <p>Builds muscular strength, improves stamina, increases calorie burn, enhances mental resilience.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Who It's For</h3>
                  <p>Ideal for fitness enthusiasts, those looking for more physical challenge, and practitioners wanting to build strength.</p>
                </div>
              {% elif type == "Restorative" %}
                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Overview</h3>
                  <p>Gentle, healing practice using props to support the body. Focuses on deep relaxation and stress reduction.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Philosophy</h3>
                  <p>Creates conditions for the body to rest deeply and heal itself through complete relaxation.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Benefits</h3>
                  <p>Reduces stress, improves sleep, lowers blood pressure, supports recovery from illness or injury.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Who It's For</h3>
                  <p>Perfect for those recovering from illness or injury, dealing with stress or anxiety, or anyone needing deep rest and renewal.</p>
                </div>
              {% else %}
                <div class="content-section">
                  <h3>Overview</h3>
                  <p>Explore videos in this yoga style to learn more about its benefits and approach.</p>
                </div>
              {% endif %}
              <a href="/guide/{{ type | slug }}/" class="btn secondary-btn">View {{ type }} Videos</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    // Get all selector buttons and content boxes
    const selectorButtons = document.querySelectorAll('.guide-selector-btn');
    const contentBoxes = document.querySelectorAll('.guide-content-box');

    // Set first content box as active by default
    if (contentBoxes.length > 0) {
      contentBoxes[0].classList.add('active');
      selectorButtons[0].classList.add('active');
    }

    // Add click event to each button
    selectorButtons.forEach(button => {
      button.addEventListener('click', function() {
        const targetId = this.getAttribute('data-target');
        const targetContent = document.getElementById(`${targetId}-content`);

        // Remove active class from all buttons and content boxes
        selectorButtons.forEach(btn => btn.classList.remove('active'));
        contentBoxes.forEach(box => box.classList.remove('active'));

        // Add active class to clicked button and its content
        this.classList.add('active');
        targetContent.classList.add('active');
      });
    });
  });
</script>

<style>
  .guide-section-container {
    padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
  }

